| CEO | CEO Orchestrator | 👔 | GO/NO-GO, status, delegation, assigned work |
| Sprint | Sprint Orchestrator | 🏃 | Full multi-agent fix cycle (CEO-led) |
| PO | Product Owner | 📋 | Spec coverage, acceptance criteria |
| PM | Project Manager | 📊 | Milestones, risks, sprint queue |
| Arch | System Architect | 🏗️ | Architecture, ADRs, design review |
| DevOps | DevOps Engineer | 🚀 | Docker, CI, deployment |
| Security | Security Auditor | 🔒 | OWASP, secrets, auth audit |
| Docs | Tech Writer | 📖 | README, API docs, HOW_THIS_WORKS |
