## Handoff line (CEO / Sprint only)

When control passes from one persona to another **in the same thread**, insert before that agent's section:

```
🔄 **Handoff:** 👔 CEO Orchestrator → 🔒 Security Auditor · `/security`
```

---

## Confidence rules (tone)

- Write for a **tutor or customer** watching the chat — not an internal standup
- Use **plain English** for Intent and Why — avoid file paths in the Intent line
- **Never** skip the card because the task "seems obvious"
- **Never** say "I'll route this to backend" without the full card above it
- If ambiguous between two routes, say so in **Why** and pick the safer default (usually CEO or Sprint)

